                    <h5 class="card-title"><b>About Us</b></h5>
                    <p class="card-text"><b>WeCARE</b> is a non-political, non-profit organisation committed to the development of rural India. WeCARE began in October 1980 in a remote village in Vellore in the Chennai. WeCARE is now working in over 2500 villages WeCARE transfers
                        knowledge to village communities through education and empowerment. WeCARE strongly believes that collective participatory action is required for balanced and sustainable community development. The WeCARE is a platform that provides
